  "2148210": {
    "name": "Divine Legacy: Neo Amburia",
    "steam_appid": 2148210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/1394e1f3bba62612e3bee446d3140b85.avif?t=1737666049\" width=618 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/edde1e2dcd99a729d742a57b5ba9005d.avif?t=1737666049\" width=618 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Divine Legacy: Neo Amburia</strong> is a medieval-fantasy RPG where a young woman must save her childhood friend, who’s been pulled toward a dark fate. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With little more than determination, she'll battle powerful foes, form unexpected alliances, and uncover secrets that could reshape the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>A New Story, A New Path</strong><br><i>Discover what happens when the villains win.</i> This is the direct sequel to <strong>Divine Legacy</strong>, following the &quot;bad end&quot; of the original game and exploring how the world would have turned out if the antagonists succeeded.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-rich experience</strong>: While the focus is on gameplay, the narrative is woven into the experience. If you're all about action, you might find yourself skipping some dialogues—but the story’s there to enrich the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/e392b89565f5569815e0d5925769369f.poster.avif?t=1737666049\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/e392b89565f5569815e0d5925769369f.webm?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/e392b89565f5569815e0d5925769369f.mp4?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character-driven world</strong>: The world was crafted with the characters in mind, not the other way around. Their personalities and backstories are at the heart of the world’s design, making every corner feel connected to who they are.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-Paced, Real-Time Combat</strong><br>Engage in <i>high-octane, action-packed</i> battles with a unique Bullet-Hell combat feel. Fight enemies with precision and speed as you dodge and weave through intense encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Playable Characters</strong> <br>Play as <strong>three distinct characters</strong>, each with a unique combat style. Choose the right one for the situation and swap them out on the fly for even more tactical options!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/651fdcc534b69484faf0b1d591b31ad8.poster.avif?t=1737666049\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/651fdcc534b69484faf0b1d591b31ad8.webm?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/651fdcc534b69484faf0b1d591b31ad8.mp4?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crafting, Potions, and Time Management</strong><br>Master <strong>combat tool crafting</strong>, potion brewing, and time-based shopping. Strategy and preparation are key to surviving the hardest fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/164c55f7b2073a429d06a90d7a13f9c5.poster.avif?t=1737666049\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/164c55f7b2073a429d06a90d7a13f9c5.webm?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/164c55f7b2073a429d06a90d7a13f9c5.mp4?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Element-Based Magic System</strong><br>Harness the power of elemental magic to dominate your enemies. Swap characters and use your arsenal of combat tools to exploit weaknesses for maximum damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/8d33d58f2a00b4d1e017502518fd83ca.poster.avif?t=1737666049\" width=576 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/8d33d58f2a00b4d1e017502518fd83ca.webm?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/8d33d58f2a00b4d1e017502518fd83ca.mp4?t=1737666049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Post-Story Content</strong><br>The adventure doesn’t end after the credits roll. Unlock additional content and challenges that keep the game fresh even after completing the main storyline.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Silly Easter Eggs &amp; References</strong><br>Expect <strong>plenty of inside jokes</strong> and nods to games, movies, and pop culture. It's serious when it needs to be... and hilarious when it doesn't!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/95a0e144a4749397c5852cb94aad76fa.webp?t=1737666049\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras_big/95a0e144a4749397c5852cb94aad76fa.avif?t=1737666049 width=800 height=55 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Developer’s Journey</strong><br><strong>Developed by One Person</strong> – <strong>Made with a lot of caffeine, some sleep deprivation, and a healthy dose of stubbornness.</strong> It’s a labor of love — raw, imperfect, but filled with passion. If you appreciate indie games that wear their heart on their sleeve, this one’s for you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NOTES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You might need to disable Steam Input for controllers to work properly, or try another template.</p></li></ul>",
